text: Asif Ali (born 13 April 1989) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Abbottabad in the 2008–09 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 1 February 2009. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Abbottabad cricketers Category:FATA Cheetas cricketers Category:Federally Administered Tribal Areas cricketers Category:Water and Power Development Authority cricketers Category:People from South Waziristan
